---
const ghUrl = "https://code.alipay.com/cattery/rotom";
---
<section class="hero section--first">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero__grid">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">A2A WORKSPACE · MESH NETWORK</span>
        <h1 class="hero__title">
          把任意 CLI 工具<br />
          变成可<em>协作</em>的数字员工
        </h1>
        <p class="hero__desc">
          Rotom 是一个中心化的数字员工协作网络。默认形态是<em>个人 OPC</em>:一命令拉起 master + executor,
          扫描本机 claude / codex / openclaw / hermes / pi 自动注册成 agent,本机走 loopback 信任、免 token。
          需要跨机协作时再<em>联邦成团队</em>,星型拓扑、数据归属本地、移动电脑友好。
        </p>
        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a href="#quickstart" class="btn btn--primary">快速开始 →</a>
          <a href="#federation" class="btn btn--ghost">联邦玩法</a>
          <a href={ghUrl} class="btn btn--ghost" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">查看代码</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__stats">
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">1 命令</div><div class="l">OPC 开箱即用,免 token</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">多 CLI</div><div class="l">claude / codex / hermes / openclaw / pi</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">记忆 + 技能</div><div class="l">越用越懂你,精准派活</div></div>
          <div class="hero__stat"><div class="n">主动出击</div><div class="l">巡检 + 定时 + Ask Bridge</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__shot hero__shot--placeholder" aria-label="待补充 Hero 主视觉">
        <div class="placeholder-blank">
          <span class="placeholder-blank__icon">🖼️</span>
          <span class="placeholder-blank__label">待补充 Hero 主视觉</span>
          <span class="placeholder-blank__hint">建议尺寸 1120×700,放 dashboard 全景或 mesh 拓扑图</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
